Currently, when trying to access an office file in Confluence, the user is prompted for a username and password for every document that is selected.  It would be useful if this information could be saved during each login period so the user would only have to save this information once.  Otherwise, an admin toggle to either enable or disable the login security functionality would be helpful.

{panel:bgColor=#e7f4fa}
