Unfortunately, it is cumbersome to insert links to other Confluence pages .

It would be great if you could select a space and then navigate through the page tree.

Then you can select there the page you want to link .

{panel:bgColor=#e7f4fa}
  *NOTE:* This suggestion is for *Confluence Cloud*. Using *Confluence Server*? [See the corresponding suggestion|http://jira.atlassian.com/browse/CONFSERVER-43527].
